posterous-js.js

Contributors:
Bryan Grohman, bgrohman@gmail.com

About:
This is an open source javascript library for using the Posterous API.
http://posterous.com/api

* Note: This project currently requires jquery 1.3.2.
http://jquery.com/

Current Functionality (version 1.0.0):
* getSites - returns information about each Posterous site for the user
* getPosts - returns information including the post body for posts for a 
	     given Posterous site
* getImages - returns images and image info from posts from a given site
